title: Secrets And Lies - S01E04 - The Track 4.avi
description:
Secrets And Lies - S01E04 - The Track 4

Now in possession of the murder weapon, Ben tries to return to a normal life until he can safely get rid of it. By chance, he stumbles onto evidence of a sexual predator living in his street, and, finally convinced that he knows who killed Thom, he takes the opportunity - but in his haste, his wife catches him destroying the evidence.
